@Daedalus' Obelisk
/i/i/i
And so, peace was restored to the land!
Eric returned home to his normal life,
although things never looked quite the
same again!

Is Daedalus truly defeated? Will Eric ever
be called to heroism again in the land of
Dagda?

Only time will tell!
#die

